FOR PROCESS A	7	4	3
FOR PROCESS B	1	2	2
FOR PROCESS C	6	0	0
FOR PROCESS D	0	1	1
FOR PROCESS E	4	3	1
ENTER THE RESOURCE IMSTANCES10 5 7
AVAILABLE:3	3	2	
